{"title":"儿歌　送哥参加自卫战","authors":["蔡牧"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":9,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送哥参加自卫战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半夜公鸡喔喔啼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和嫂嫂起五更"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥明儿去参战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶早给他烙几张饼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂切葱花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把面来和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葱花切得针细五分长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面儿和得软柔耐手摸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来拉风箱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灶心火发笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火呀火呀你猜错了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这会儿没客来，是咱送哥哥……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饼儿烙得薄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饼儿烙得圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饼儿烙得两面黄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包俺哥哥吃来香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饼儿烙成千层空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面包上芝麻盐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千层饼里千层心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大我去参加八路军……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}